## Third-Party Components

Blackboard AI incorporates several third-party open-source components, each with its own license:

1. **Manim** - Mathematical Animation Engine: MIT License
   - https://github.com/ManimCommunity/manim/blob/main/LICENSE

2. **Coqui TTS** - Text-to-Speech Library: MPL-2.0 License 
   - https://github.com/coqui-ai/TTS/blob/main/LICENSE.txt

3. **PythonKit** - Swift framework for Python interoperability: Apache License 2.0
   - https://github.com/pvieito/PythonKit/blob/master/LICENSE.txt

4. **OpenAI API** - Usage governed by OpenAI's Terms of Use
   - https://openai.com/policies/terms-of-use

